_aFiles._sDescription: The Map, What Else Would It Be?

_sText:
I found a disturbing lack of actually detailed and semi-realistic arena maps for CSS, most of them were
tough on the eyes and either simply used dev-grids or bright custom textures. 

For this map I made a relatively same size arena whilst incorporating the same features of similar, I also added grayer(ish) textures to make it more light on the eyes and fit CSS's general aesthetic.
